<div id="pf22ab" class="pf w33 h124" data-page-no="22ab"><div class="pc pc22ab w33 h124"><div class="t m18b7 x5d h57 y1f66 ff1 fs22 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FAR EASTERN </div><div class="t m1d0a x63 h57 y1b50 ff1 fs22 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DIVISION </div><div class="t m6fd x59 h22 y165c ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THIRTEENTH SABBATH OFFERING </div><div class="t m1f1 x35 h22 y1f5b ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Far Eastern Division â€” December 28 </div><div class="t m1533 x15 h6d y1b15 ff1 fs12 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">S</div><div class="t m21c0 x71 h22 y1ee3 ff1 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">EVEN </div><div class="t m428 x6f h4 y1dd9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">long war-weary years have passed since our latest Thirteenth Sab-</div><div class="t mde7 x5d h4 y14f8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bath Offering overflow was dedicated to the Far Eastern Division. It </div><div class="t mc4 x15 h4 y1b73 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">amounted to $7,742.63, and gave encouragement to the brethren and strength </div><div class="t ma53 x15 h4 y1cb7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the work. In the intervening years our institutions, churches, and the </div><div class="t m110 x15 h4 y1d5f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">homes of our people have suffered from war&apos;s awful scourge. Publishing </div><div class="t m22d x15 h4 y1c97 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">houses, colleges and academies, and church buildings have been destroyed, or </div><div class="t m748 x15 h4 y1ced ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">so greatly damaged as to be unusable. In the Philippines alone 116 of our </div><div class="t m5f2 x15 h4 y1374 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">churches were destroyed, together with the sanitarium, publishing house, and </div><div class="t mf37 x15 h4 y1b00 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">three academies. Notwithstanding war&apos;s horrors and hindrances eight thou-</div><div class="t m6da x15 h4 y2114 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sand persons were baptized in this division during the war years. </div><div class="t m695 x4a h4 y2141 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The needs are vast and urgent. Calls multiply for workers. Money, much </div><div class="t mdff x15 h4 y1cab ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">money, is needed to restore all lines of work and press on into fruitful fields </div><div class="t m22a x27 h4 y1831 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of evangelism. Two hundred and thirty-five million people must hear the </div><div class="t m7b7 x15 h4 y180c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;good news.&quot; And thirty-six thousand Seventh-day Adventists throughout the </div><div class="t m72a x27 h4 y1b03 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">division are sacrificing with us to hasten the finishing of the task. The &quot;over-</div><div class="t m172 x27 h4 y229d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">flow&quot; offering on December 28 should be the largest we have ever given, and </div><div class="t mb66 x27 h4 y236f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it will be if every member will double what he has given in the past. </div><div class="t m599 x2e h13 y1d43 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 40 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
